@startuml Context Diagram

package "ConversationService" {
  [ConversationService] as CS
}

package "External Systems" {
  [API Gateway] as Gateway
  [Ollama Service] as Ollama
  [Database] as DB
  [Redis Cache] as Redis
  [Frontend Applications] as Frontend
}

' External Interactions
Frontend --> Gateway : HTTP Requests
Gateway --> CS : Authenticated Requests
CS --> Ollama : Model Inference
CS --> DB : Data Persistence
CS --> Redis : Caching

note right of CS
  The ConversationService:
  - Manages chat conversations
  - Handles message history
  - Provides real-time chat
  - Integrates with Ollama
end note

@enduml 